Thousand Oaks: 15.5% Simi Valley: 14.9% Ventura: 13.8% Camarillo: 7.8% 
Moorpark: 3.8% Santa Paula: 3.7% Port Hueneme: 3.0% Fillmore: 1.7% Ojai: 1.1% 
