 USAir Held Liable for Fatal Crash: A federal judge in Cleveland ruled USAir 
Group Inc. is financially liable for the March, 1992, crash in which 27 people 
died at New York's La Guardia Airport. Families of those killed and survivors 
are seeking compensation for the crash, and awards will be determined later.The 
company said it could not estimate what the cost may be, and has said it would 
