<P>
 Atlantic Richfield Co. announced that Executive Vice President William E. Wade 
Jr. will now run all of Arco's exploration and production operations, including 
Arco Alaska Inc. 
</P>
<P>
 The Los Angeles-based oil company also announced that Executive Vice President 
James A. Middleton, who had been in charge of the Alaska operations, will 
continue to run Arco Products Co. and Arco Transportation Co., as well as 
taking on Arco Coal Co. and Arco Aluminum Inc., which had previously been under 
Wade. 
</P>
<P>
